data.description: Welcome to your new home in the beautiful Stonebridge subdivision! This unique property features a creatively designed floor plan that offers endless possibilities for customization. The home boasts a formal dining room, a spacious kitchen, and a great backyard - perfect for hosting guests. There's a multipurpose converted garage with a private entrance that can be used as a home office, rec room, or lounge.  The Primary Bedroom has an en suite and double closets. The fourth bedroom opens up into the third, providing you with the flexibility to use the space in any way you desire!  Plus, the entire upstairs has been freshly painted with new carpet, while the Primary Bedroom bathroom and hallway bathroom have new vinyl flooring and countertops.  This move-in ready home is equipped with 2 zoned heating and cooling systems, and a mini split that heats/cools as well. Priced to sell, this home is a steal, as the seller have already secured their next home. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful property your own!
